---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "13 march 2026";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="prompt-line">
        <span class="prompt">cat /etc/root/privacy.txt</span>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="meta-block">
            <p>REVISION: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>

        <section>
            <h2>01. DATA_CONTROLLER_SPEC</h2>
            <p>
                The Data Controller (Art. 4 (7) GDPR) is <strong>Alexander Samuelsen-Manso</strong>. 
                Interaction with xelA (Site or Bot) constitutes full agreement to these 
                processing protocols.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>02. COLLECTION_VECTORS</h2>
            <div class="sub-module">
                <h3>HTTP_ENDPOINT [https://droot.is-a.dev]</h3>
                <p>
                    Automatic metadata collection: IP addresses, access timestamps, and page URI. 
                    Used strictly for DDoS prevention and service recovery. 
                    <strong>No tracking cookies are deployed.</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="sub-module">
                <h3>DISCORD_GATEWAY [root Bot]</h3>
                <p>
                    Real-time message processing occurs to provide moderation and command execution. 
                    Data persistence is triggered only by specific opt-in modules. 
                    <strong>Removing the bot triggers a permanent guild-data wipe.</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>03. PERSISTENCE_LOG [RETENTION_SCHEDULE]</h2>
            <pre class="data-table">
TYPE                | DURATION          | PURPOSE
--------------------|-------------------|------------------
Interaction Logs    | when bot restarts | Debugging/Support
Support Tickets     | 1-3 Months        | History/Reference
Message Manager     | 30 Days           | Mod Audit-Trail
Moderation Events   | 1 Year            | Guild Enforcement
System Errors       | Indefinite        | Resolution Only
            </pre>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>04. DATA_PROCESSOR_ROLES</h2>
            <p>
                For the <strong>Message Manager Service</strong>, root operates as a 
                <span class="tag">DATA_PROCESSOR</span>. The Server Owner is the 
                <span class="tag">DATA_CONTROLLER</span>.
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Owners must inform users of active message logging.</li>
                <li>Data is not profiled, analyzed, or shared with third parties.</li>
                <li>Non-compliance results in immediate API access revocation.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>05. SUBJECT_RIGHTS [GDPR_INVOKE]</h2>
            <p>To execute the following protocols, contact the root administrator:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>RIGHT_OF_ACCESS: View all stored metadata.</li>
                <li>RIGHT_TO_ERASURE: Request immediate DB purge.</li>
                <li>DATA_PORTABILITY: Request a full JSON/CSV archive.</li>
                <li>RIGHT_TO_OBJECT: Restrict active processing.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-footer">
            <h2>06. CONTACT_CHANNEL</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>EMAIL: snowwy@danbot.host</li>
                <li>DISCORD: <a href="https://droot.is-a.dev/help">https://droot.is-a.dev/help</a></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .prompt-line {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-family: monospace;
    }

    .legal-content {
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .meta-block {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        padding: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--terminal-pink);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .legal-content h1 {
        font-family: monospace;
        color: var(--terminal-pink);
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .legal-content h2 {
        color: var(--terminal-blue);
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--terminal-blue);
        padding-left: 10px;
    }

    .sub-module h3 {
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--terminal-pink);
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .data-table {
        background: #0d0d0d;
        padding: 1rem;
        color: #a0a0a0;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .tag {
        background: var(--terminal-blue);
        color: #000;
        padding: 1px 5px;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .legal-content ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
    }

    .legal-content li {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .legal-content li::before {
        content: "→";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--terminal-pink);
    }

    .contact-footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }
</style>